edBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"點解要雙胞胎？去之前同去之後嘅DNA 對比唔得咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"咁你點confirm 去前去後既改變一定係因為去咗太空? 可能佢喺地球都會有呢啲改變 無人知，所以要搵雙胞胎"},{"pid":"ea6cc7bd6dab3d8d0b8a9ffc92dcb8c9916a1d41","tid":596863,"uid":13343,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"8fe602b0ca88ec45b0983d16abfc065045c33177","tid":596863,"uid":76053,"like":91,"dislike":0,"score":91,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T05:59:47.000Z","msg":"應該只係epigenetic 變化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T06:57:16.000Z","msg":"Gene expression level 有唔同到<br />\n<br />\n其實應該只係飲食/重力/ 輻射嘅stress 影響到<br />\n<br />\n裡面有提有d gene expression lv 過咗兩日就回復正常<br />\n<br />\n但係有d keep咗一排都未回復"},{"pid":"7557122bdd0fa8be43418cbd3b641238323d1ce9","tid":596863,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"alternative splicing <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99d922314621da857258e5f1862925f002a5d8f","tid":596863,"uid":392,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"新類型人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfa9d3ee460da3bff00823a422c750d3a017bca","tid":596863,"uid":77968,"like":4,"dislike":84,"score":-80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T07:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nerdist.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/The-Thing-cosmic-horror.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnerdist.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FThe-Thing-cosmic-horror.jpg&h=59a43a18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f92f340b387bd5bb4bca12769dc57ea9f6a41c88","tid":596863,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T07:16:42.000Z","msg":"即刻靚仔咗"},{"pid":"36496c012c78e8a9f4c01a173c1aff1837b2d377","tid":596863,"uid":21699,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T07