msg":"咁你點confirm 去前去後既改變一定係因為去咗太空? 可能佢喺地球都會有呢啲改變 無人知，所以要搵雙胞胎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"咁你點confirm唔可以留o係地球既人因為經歷左某d野變左基因<br />\n而唔係上太空果個變"},{"pid":"6fc38f35b1fcc3fc9ed30965e73c2bc675301659","tid":596863,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4b961e19af52ebd38a4f84f3ca6daf3c1fcd7d","tid":596863,"uid":48152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"變唔奇 係估唔到一年時間就變7%<br />\n如果生活大半世唔知會點"},{"pid":"360205187e66f8fe1904d7b964e48f09ba5a1b2f","tid":596863,"uid":31901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"火星異種"},{"pid":"399d71224710674ab2c11d7e197ea4e88d690f8e","tid":596863,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>滅絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即刻諗起"},{"pid":"15967a681732218b814f7423a6b1727b0864170d","tid":596863,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26a5d95bddd9e07d21bdf2dd254dcb117f67cc78","tid":596863,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐仲未有嘉美尤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"我生得聰明得罪你咩"},{"pid":"44682b260bfad526ad2f6edbf597433f1a329d8e","tid":596863,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"寶少幾時誕生"},{"pid":"86e036ab6c546fa9d0c54415c586fe708a775118","tid":596863,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://geneonline.news/index.php/2018/03/16/nasa-twins-study-space-gene/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgeneonline.news%2Findex.php%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2Fnasa-twins-study-space-gene%2F&d=iZYmbYB9RV8p5MHDbqQo6hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=946e4d77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://geneonline.news/index.php/2018/03/16/nasa-twins-study-space-gene/</a><br />\n解讀雙胞胎實驗新結果！\b 改變的是「太空基因」表現而非序列本身！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信許多人對 Mark Kelly 和 Scott Kelly 這雙胞胎太空人實驗還記憶猶新，美國太空總署（NASA）為了研究外太空對人體的影響，讓 Scott 於 2015～2016 年期間，在國際太空站上生活 340 天，而他的雙胞胎哥哥 Mark 則留在地球上當作控制組，並定期於實驗前、中、後等階段，收集他們的一些血液樣本及身體資訊，進行分析研究。<br />\n<br />\n近日，NASA 公布更進一步的結果，Scott 在回到地球 6 個月後，雖然 DNA 序列本身沒有改變，但仍有 7％ 基因表現（特定 DNA 片段的活性，也就是基因產生 mRNA 的情形）產生變化未恢復。這些未恢復的基因表現被稱為&ldquo;太空基因&rdquo;，可能與 Scott 的免疫系統、DNA修復、骨形成、缺氧（hypoxia）和高碳酸血症（hypercapnia）有關。<br />\n<br />\n加州大學遺傳學家 Nichole Holm 表示，Mark 和 Scott 仍然是非常相同的雙胞胎， 因為產生變化的是 Scott 的 mRNA ，而不是他的 DNA。因此，二兄弟的 DNA 仍然幾乎完全相同，而且與其他地球上的人相比更加相似。<br />\n<br />\nNASA 也指出，研究團隊觀察到基因表現的變化，就是人類身體對環境的反應，當人類處於特定壓力下，如登山或潛水，也會產生類似的變化。約翰霍普金斯大學（Johns Hopkins University）醫學院副教授 Dan Arking 也指出，如果人類長時間在高海拔地區生活，你會看到基因表現的差異，例如，你的血液中有更多的紅血球，這是因為缺氧會影響你的基因表現。<br />\n<br />\n此外，NASA 也指出，Scott 於太空時，其血管發炎的生物標記和水通道蛋白2（aquaporin-2，AQP2）立即升高，而且頸動脈壁也增厚，但 Mark 沒有觀察到變化，表示太空旅行也會影響血管發炎、人體尿液調節。但回到地球之後，Scott  也恢復正常。這種適應是可逆的，代表未來需要更多來研究來進一步探討。<br />\n<br />\nNASA 與其他研究團隊預計今年夏天將會公佈更為全面的雙胞胎研究結果。"},{"pid":"5d091d4edb483f54f71c68bf6dfbeae3783465fd","tid":596863,"uid":55628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"純種變革者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f060bdf58ac59670ce6c3a95d3aae8d02802a5ef","tid":596863,"uid":4519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"New type<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75e138ce84809078bcbfc4ded401b2abc9a43fb","tid":596863,"uid":33650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"New type原來係真"},{"pid":"4863a0c213a096d379071de96444c52170fcd5e5","tid":596863,"uid":142231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ea258f91aec71a63b8a55d122aa94b1052159b4","tid":596863,"uid":148599,"like":7,"dislike":22,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T06:54:51.000Z","msg":"進化論？新人類？<br />\n一直認為人類既歸宿始終係係太空，地球既引力將人類既野心同可能束縳住，幾時先到下個太空文明，好想太空旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"你係咪馬沙？"},{"pid":"08e7edaadcfe4815f165eef39be0ca33374dea82","tid":596863,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"變new type裸靈不是夢"},{"pid":"78a15efe35d04498fe627c7ea28d7f2a88460178","tid":596863,"uid":36964,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"36496c012c78e8a9f4c01a173c1aff1837b2d377","tid":596863,"uid":21699,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"加州大學遺傳學家 Nichole Holm 表示，Mark 和 Scott 仍然是非常相同的雙胞胎， <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為產生變化的是 Scott 的 mRNA ，而不是他的 DNA。</span></span>因此，二兄弟的 DNA 仍然幾乎完全相同，而且與其他地球上的人相比更加相似。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦 連登班毒撚同波台狗識撚mRNA wikiepdia都唔會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a182d90a4fb0fc9c7428791289629200e45be5","tid":596863,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">宇宙射線</span><br />\n根據美國航空航天局（NASA）的估計，航天員在太陽系內的太空中每年受到250 mSv的輻射，體內約有1/3的DNA會被宇宙射線切斷。[4]在月面是70-120mSv/y，近地軌道是100mSv/y，范艾倫輻射帶為15 Sv/y。太陽也會釋放大量質子與重原子核，以接近光速噴出，有時一小時內會逾數Sv，對沒有屏障的航天員是致死劑量。"},{"pid":"c044d84754642b3ccd21c01a5b91422718f99d42","tid":596863,"uid":74207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9935d885f5f09b9a59b6a3be7e21747439839c1d","tid":596863,"uid":64129,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"b7735e37cfde4bcfc35a1aa3cc754ad246d59aab","tid":596863,"uid":35698,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"c1d6879eb5f8c9bedb5dca39c19d23a83a450f91","tid":596863,"uid":113178,"